{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331130/extras/steam_basic_info_pic-01-01.png?t=1734694038\" /><strong>Just Another Night Shift is a casual competitive 1v1 and 2v2 PvP multiplayer online game.</strong> You get to play as a security guard and a thief. The Thief\u2019s objective is to steal a specific item from the mansion, while the Guard tries to stop him. Join us for hours of fun gameplay with your friends! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Basics Of the Game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The winner of the game is whoever wins the set amount of rounds first.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Players switch sides at the middle of the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Both characters have strengths and weaknesses, and a special ability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The Guard has additional tasks, he must feed the fish, protect the cheese and water the exotic plant. If he fails to do so, the Thief will win the round.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331130/extras/play_as_a_thief-04.png?t=1734694038\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331130/extras/play_as_a_thief_compresse_new.gif?t=1734694038\" /><strong>Sneak into the mansion and steal the statue! Buy useful items from the black market, use the Thiefs agility and special hiding ability to avoid the Guard. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331130/extras/play_as_a_guard-05.png?t=1734694038\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331130/extras/play_as_a_guard_compressed.gif?t=1734694038\" /><strong>Guard the mansion and catch the Thief! Use the dog or the cameras to gain advantage over the Thief. Remember to do the tasks, light the shadows with the flashlight and buy helpful items from the security shop.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Attention!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The game works using a peer-to-peer (P2P) system. Player 1 works as a server and the player 2 as a client. Over long distances between these two you may expect high latency and problems in the game.</i></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2331130?t=1734694038","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331130/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1734694038","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331130/fc586fa32a1c04fa12ba682bec321d266cef2256/capsule_231x87_alt_assets_1.jpg?t=1734694038","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331130/fc586fa32a1c04fa12ba682bec321d266cef2256/capsule_184x69_alt_assets_1.jpg?t=1734694038","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Follow Us On</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331130/extras/steamhiiri-03.png?t=1734694038\" /> <br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331130/extras/steam_basic_info_pic-01-01.png?t=1734694038\" /><strong>Just Another Night Shift is a casual competitive 1v1 and 2v2 PvP multiplayer online 